  sectionId (71792)
  sectionNo (45)
  orderNo 46
  title Repealed.
  content obj_root_law_sections_45_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_45_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00109_187618_1666091274292&sectionId=71792&sectionno=45&orderno=46&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00109_187618_1666091274292
obj_root_law_sections_45_content:
  string
  line `45. Power to create new districts. Power to form sub-divisions of districts. ---Rep .by the United`
  line `Provinces Act, 1890 (20 of 1890), s. 35.`
obj_root_law_sections_45_footnotes:
